Properties Util::KaapiComponentManager::prop [static]

Defaut properties for the processus This table is initialized on return to the call to Util::KaapiComponentManager::initialize and contains definitions of values for the key definied for the parser Util::KaapiComponentManager::parser. It could be used by all KaapiComponent during the invocation to initialize methods.
